---
// Features Section
---

<section id="features" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
		<div class="text-center mb-16 animate-fade-in">
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
				Fitur Utama
			</h2>
			<div class="w-24 h-1 bg-raga-green mx-auto mb-8"></div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
			<!-- Feature 1 -->
			<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 animate-slide-up">
				<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-raga-green to-green-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
					<i class="fas fa-eye text-white text-2xl"></i>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Deteksi Gerakan Real-time</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
					Sistem mendeteksi dan menganalisis gerakan tubuh secara real-time menggunakan webcam standar dengan akurasi tinggi.
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Feature 2 -->
			<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 animate-slide-up">
				<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
					<i class="fas fa-fist-raised text-white text-2xl"></i>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Beragam Gestur Aksi</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
					Mendukung berbagai gerakan: Pukulan Kanan, Pukulan Kiri, Tendangan Kanan, Tendangan Kiri, Bertahan, dan Melompat.
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Feature 3 -->
			<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 animate-slide-up">
				<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
					<i class="fas fa-gamepad text-white text-2xl"></i>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Kontrol Game Langsung</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
					Gerakan fisik langsung dikonversi menjadi input keyboard untuk mengontrol karakter dalam game Tekken 6.
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Feature 4 -->
			<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 animate-slide-up">
				<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
					<i class="fas fa-tv text-white text-2xl"></i>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Umpan Balik Visual</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
					Interface yang menampilkan feedback visual real-time untuk membantu pengguna memahami gerakan yang terdeteksi.
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Feature 5 -->
			<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 animate-slide-up">
				<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500 to-red-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
					<i class="fas fa-universal-access text-white text-2xl"></i>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Aksesibilitas Tinggi</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
					Dapat digunakan oleh berbagai kalangan tanpa memerlukan perangkat khusus, hanya webcam standar.
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Feature 6 -->
			<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 animate-slide-up">
				<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-teal-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
					<i class="fas fa-cogs text-white text-2xl"></i>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Konfigurasi Fleksibel</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
					Sistem dapat dikalibrasi dan disesuaikan dengan preferensi dan kondisi fisik masing-masing pengguna.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>